A vibrant Studio Ghibli style illustration of a festive Chinese New Year scene in Singapore, featuring traditional red paper lanterns glowing warmly against a twilight sky, golden mandarin oranges piled in ornate ceramic bowls, delicate cherry blossom branches with soft pink petals drifting in the breeze, and red envelopes scattered artfully on a wooden table. In the background, traditional shophouses with intricate architectural details line a quiet street, their facades decorated with red banners and golden ornaments. The atmosphere is magical and celebratory, with soft warm lighting creating a dreamy, nostalgic mood characteristic of Hayao Miyazaki's artistic vision, emphasizing rich reds, golds, and warm amber tones throughout the composition.
